{"type":"message","id":"51f234fb","parentId":"5858caee","timestamp":"2026-04-17T00:59:53.980Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-17 08:59:50 GMT+8] Feishu[coding-agent] DM | 张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae) [msg:om_x100b512c2e9df8a4c38522fbd1d677d]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b512c2e9df8a4c38522fbd1d677d\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-17 08:59 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\n道指+0.24%、标普500+0.26%、纳指+0.36%怎么能推断出来隔夜全球股市偏弱 — 美股恒指小幅收涨但力度有限，全球风险偏好未明显修复，成长/高估值题材仍承压；优先关注黄金、军工、能源、高股息方向。"}],"timestamp":1776387593977}}
{"type":"message","id":"7aa0eff6","parentId":"51f234fb","timestamp":"2026-04-17T01:00:08.275Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating market report skills**\n\nThe user asked about stock market interpretation, and I’m trying to determine which skill applies. While it might not need a tool, I think the news-market skill could be relevant since it generates global market morning news. The user’s question seems to be about the logic behind a report, so I should read the news-market skill more closely. I'll keep it conversational and succinct in my response while addressing the assertion.\n\n**Explaining market conclusions**\n\nI could clarify that just from the modest gains in three U.S. indices, you can't directly conclude that \"global equities are weak.\" This conclusion needs a broader context involving cross-asset data and market breadth. For example, the gains are small and may be a technical rebound after a sharp drop. Additionally, if risk-on assets underperform defensives, like semiconductors being weaker than energy, it paints a different picture. The elevated VIX and rising U.S. yields also indicate a non-traditional risk-on environment.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_06c3af14b50a39800169e1860c67d4819b817cb17123a21a4e\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp4YYXpMzCBrlpcSJvWWgp_cGxgea8cWE428kvTijblpGhwccZuEQFxClKCFYrIuRTYt6fuFeegmPaMloNF92yjnzi0ziLhPwPUeQ53j5RK455KCpAz8r_KiYHJcs8WvVZxSnZOhkCS3ogzIHjhoYPZ3e6xZZta7oErKbdLfxUSqKLDcaVvjluAv9pJAq2If0Ni9oWyE1L1C9zHNc4IJ3Ccce5OgoHUzqNYGh6_K0PUjHsl-zHBTOgd_S1lDu7lQBG4oMgPQD9Og6F7jvCsYJqL1NHLz__BumBe-B8_7beyaFNkAt8T382CDzufim9CzAm4AbLAxpUXWYocKKpI6I232DE0PGHfJopPozkY09YD-JSvHnDXLOazcZ-EHCAQ2_L8F_0_ymfMqEQEA_2iyDNMWM-1l8hc-Tb3_QHezVViZfW9lWHfGEUTL8Iu-CbMLLgsipsv9YuKSLtd0EK3ltbHyP-0VaWj8QdXPTVcmPrv_8_fmSRCrwQ6a88dMgh9twJkf2m9C43v1Fil0Z6xQcncBIwv8CqNZHuLwg8HvZSKE1WxucFIfTxrJw-QKhTFmE-wOxa6IqcmRpbvLkNpE2qirysyCX39Jg37sUbae4z2iUtt4_QBRaTiqjnEM0uXRJDqVoY31K