rt options**\\n\\nI’m noticing there’s no morning report in this skill. Maybe I need to check a different skill or see if I can locate a global phrase in the logs or another repository. It could also be something generated by the news-market skill in my skills directory. I'll need to inspect that directory and figure out what’s going on. Let’s see what I can uncover!\"}]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_yXGZMmspv2bCuV2Q8QIQjW1x|fc_06c3af14b50a39800169e186c83ea8819b8424bd51a6932a26","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find ~/.openclaw/skills/news-market -maxdepth 3 -type f | head -n 200","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent","timeout":20},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"find ~/.openclaw/skills/news-market -maxdepth 3 -type f | head -n 200\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent\",\"timeout\":20}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":38233,"output":110,"cacheRead":1536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39879,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776387775233,"responseId":"resp_06c3af14b50a39800169e186c37504819baea144bad82bb82a"}}
