t3N2ofJ61RoamVTFQl62zMRtW-nu4_M20CvOLOSp6iy_AwLM3g7tsuJ7yFU-i2RRiwyk_AAZeLJFdR153J6S_yoB6fqc7ihUDtHf1aC-sKWIuB78WsD2hob6EkkW7bAHopYuW4QScT_QBS2BpkEoWQywYpxZyOlF5zGMDgr4YQJ-rGxuU4w-Xw8u07UT5nVG3QZku9WOdxtGZ5NtCUZPg1b0NDRjGzqIcdRkdr2KWBMU2X2VwWcokWeBt9MiI_k_nM4YZrZrFxrao39fBWTXXCtaH-L0n1pyi7XMeek1JzijUD-XQBaon4I7C-NvcdL02d5x8K1aaPgcZyBrE_J5SWq8EHnFqQeaWjYO8tfpetSahK1_6SyVumb5Zv1DtXvfSn1ehWydjelzN5t4Cr4NeWafIz1OTdVZG0agel-3yx049YQBkV7nKW3RlW0imHbSJ0vIF1WBm2TRMr\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Evaluating script changes**\\n\\nI see that the current script needs some adjustments. The user might be quoting an analysis, so I think we can enhance the news-market script with a more evidence-based interpretation. They seemed open to modifying the template, which is promising. If we’re going to implement this in the news-market skill, we might also need to think about committing any changes after editing the script in the appropriate directory. But hmm, I’m not sure if committing is necessary for external edits.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Clarifying edit constraints**\\n\\nI’m considering whether we need to commit changes since the editing is happening in an external directory and not the workspace. The instructions specify committing changes in the workspace after edits, so there’s a bit of confusion. I might also want to check if a Git repository exists there since it could affect how we handle commits. If we want to update the installed skill, I'll need to ensure the logic is correct, especially for calculating overnight returns.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Enhancing global risk interpretation**\\n\\nI’m thinking about adding an `interpret_global_risk` function with an evidence chain. The user seems concerned about interpreting weak signals from small positive US gains. So, I could implement a logic framework: if the major US indexes are all over 0.5 on average and the HSI is above 0.8, we might consider it a risk-on scenario. For small positives below 0.4, I’d say there's stability but not enough to assume weakness directly. However, fetching defensive assets isn’t currently in the script, but maybe I could include GLD, USO, or XLE.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"我顺手把另一个更大的坑一起补上：它现在算的其实是“开盘到收盘的日内涨跌”，不是“相对前收的隔夜涨跌”。这会直接带偏判断。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06c3af14b50a39800169e186e24a44819bbc3e8c08d8941f9f\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_O6uSHiuwKKxGMVE6PHj8dc0u|fc_06c3af14b50a39800169e186e2fe00819b934b01a68ae01491","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/news-market/scripts/generate_morning_news.py","edits":[{"oldText":"def get_全球市场数据():\n    \"\"\"获取全球主要市场数据\"\"\"\n    markets = {\n        \"上证指数\": \"000001.SS\",\n        \"深证成指\": \"399001.SZ\",\n        \"创业板指\": \"399006.SZ\",\n        \"恒生指数\": \"^HSI\",  # 改为HSI指数\n        \"道琼斯\": \"^DJI\",\n        \"标普500\": \"^GSPC\",\n        \"纳斯达克\": \"^IXIC\",\n    }\n    \n    result = {}\n    for name, ticker in markets.items():\n        try:\n            if ticker.endswith(\".HK\"):\n                data = yf.Ticker(ticker).history(period=\"1d\")\n            else:\n                data = yf.Ticker(ticker).history(period=\"1d\")\n            \n            if len(data) > 0:\n                price = data['Close'].iloc[-1]\n                prev = data['Open'].iloc[-1]\n                change = (price - prev) / prev * 100\n                result[name] = {\"价格\": round(price, 2), \"涨跌幅\": round(change, 2)}\n        except Exception as e:\n            result[name] = {\"价格\": \"-\", \"涨跌幅\": \"-\", \"error\": str(e)}\n    \n    return result\n","newText":"def get_全球市场数据():\n    \"\"\"获取全球主要市场数据（按收盘价相对前收盘计算涨跌幅）\"\"\"\n    markets = {\n        \"上证指数\": \"000001.SS\",\n        \"深证成指\": \"399001.SZ\",\n        \"创业板指\": \"399006.SZ\",\n        \"恒生指数\": \"^HSI\",\n        \"道琼斯\": \"^DJI\",\n        \"标普500\": \"^GSPC\",\n        \"纳斯达克\": \"^IXIC\",\n    }\n\n    result = {}\n    for name, ticker in markets.items():\n        try:\n            data = yf.Ticker(ticker).history(period=\"5d\", auto_adjust=False)\n            if len(data) >= 2:\n                price = float(data['Close'].iloc[-1])\n                prev_close = float(data['Close'].iloc[-2])\n                change = (price - prev_close) / prev_close * 100 if prev_close else 0\n                result[name] = {\n                    \"价格\": round(price, 2),\n                    \"前收\": round(prev_close, 2),\n                    \"涨跌幅\": round(change, 2),\n                }\n            elif len(data) == 1:\n                price = float(data['Close'].iloc[-1])\n                result[name] = {\"价格\": round(price, 2), \"前收\": \"-\", \"涨跌幅\": \"-\"}\n            else:\n                result[name] = {\"价格\": \"-\", \"前收\": \"-\", \"涨跌幅\": \"-\", \"error\": \"无数据\"}\n        except Exception as e:\n            result[name] = {\"价格\": \"-\", \"前收\": \"-\", \"涨跌幅\": \"-\", \"error\": str(e)}\n\n    return result\n\n\ndef analyze_global_market(global_data):\n    \"\"\"基于指数表现给出保守、证据驱动的全球市场判断\"\"\"\n    us_names = [\"道琼斯\", \"标普500\", \"纳斯达克\"]\n    hk_names = [\"恒生指数\"]\n\n    us_changes = [global_data.get(name, {}).get(\"涨跌幅\") for name in us_names]\n    us_changes = [x for x in us_changes if isinstance(x, (int, float))]\n    hk_changes = [global_data.get(name, {}).get(\"涨跌幅\") for name in hk_names]\n    hk_changes = [x for x in hk_changes if isinstance(x, (int, float))]\n\n    evidence = []\n    if us_changes:\n        us_avg = sum(us_changes) / len(us_changes)\n        us_up = sum(1 for x in us_changes if x > 0)\n        evidence.append(f\"美股三大指数 {us_up}/3 收涨，平均涨幅 {us_avg:+.2f}%\")\n    else:\n        us_avg = None\n        us_up = 0\n\n    if hk_changes:\n        evidence.append(f\"恒生指数 {hk_changes[0]:+.2f}%\")\n\n    if us_avg is None:\n        summary = \"海外市场数据不足，暂不下方向性结论\"\n        tone = \"中性\"\n    elif us_up == 3 and us_avg >= 0.80:\n        summary = \"隔夜海外市场明显走强，风险偏好修复较为清晰\"\n        tone = \"偏强\"\n    elif us_up == 3 and us_avg >= 0.20:\n        summary = \"隔夜海外市场小幅修复，但力度一般，宜表述为偏稳或弱修复\"\n        tone = \"偏稳\"\n    elif us_up >= 2 and us_avg > -0.20:\n        summary = \"隔夜海外市场分化震荡，未形成明确 risk-on / risk-off 信号\"\n        tone = \"中性\"\n    elif us_avg <= -0.50:\n        summary = \"隔夜海外市场整体偏弱，风险偏好回落\"\n        tone = \"偏弱\"\n    else:\n        summary = \"隔夜海外市场略偏弱，但暂无单边走弱共识\"\n        tone = \"偏弱\"\n\n    caveat = \"仅依据主要指数涨跌判断；若需推导风格偏好，还应结合黄金、美元、美债收益率及成长/防御板块相对强弱。\"\n\n    return {\n        \"结论\": summary,\n        \"口径\": tone,\n        \"依据\": evidence,\n        \"提示\": caveat,\n    }\n"}]},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/news-market/scripts/generate_morning_news.py\",\"edits\":[{\"oldText\":\"def get_全球市场数据():\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"获取全球主要市场数据\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    markets = {\\n        \\\"上证指数\\\": \\\"000001.SS\\\",\\n        \\\"深证成指\\\": \\\"399001.SZ\\\",\\n        \\\"创业板指\\\": \\\"399006.SZ\\\",\\n        \\\"恒生指数\\\": \\\"^HSI\\\",  # 改为HSI指数\\n        \\\"道琼斯\\\": \\\"^DJI\\\",\\n        \\\"标普500\\\": \\\"^GSPC\\\",\\n        \\\"纳斯达克\\\": \\\"^IXIC\\\",\\n    }\\n    \\n    result = {}\\n    for name, ticker in markets.items():\\n        try:\\n            if ticker.endswith(\\\".HK\\\"):\\n                data = yf.Ticker(ticker).history(period=\\\"1d\\\")\\n            else:\\n                data = yf.Ticker(ticker).history(period=\\\"1d\\\")\\n            \\n            if len(data) > 0:\\n                price = data['Close'].iloc[-1]\\n                prev = data['Open'].iloc[-1]\\n                change = (price - prev) / prev * 100\\n                result[name] = {\\\"价格\\\": round(price, 2), \\\"涨跌幅\\\": round(change, 2)}\\n        except Exception as e:\\n            result[name] = {\\\"价格\\\": \\\"-\\\", \\\"涨跌幅\\\": \\\"-\\\", \\\"error\\\": str(e)}\\n    \\n    return result\\n\",\"newText\":\"def get_全球市场数据():\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"获取全球主要市场数据（按收盘价相对前收盘计算涨跌幅）\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    markets = {\\n        \\\"上证指数\\\": \\\"000001.SS\\\",\\n        \\\"深证成指\\\": \\\"399001.SZ\\\",\\n        \\\"创业板指\\\": \\\"399006.SZ\\\",\\n        \\\"恒生指数\\\": \\\"^HSI\\\",\\n        \\\"道琼斯\\\": \\\"^DJI\\\",\\n        \\\"标普500\\\": \\\"^GSPC\\\",\\n        \\\"纳斯达克\\\": \\\"^IXIC\\\",\\n    }\\n\\n    result = {}\\n    for name, ticker in markets.items():\\n        try:\\n            data = yf.Ticker(ticker).history(period=\\\"5d\\\", auto_adjust=False)\\n            if len(data) >= 2:\\n                price = float(data['Close'].iloc[-1])\\n                prev_close = float(data['Close'].iloc[-2])\\n                change = (price - prev_close) / prev_close * 100 if prev_close else 0\\n                result[name] = {\\n                    \\\"价格\\\": round(price, 2),\\n                    \\\"前收\\\": round(prev_close, 2),\\n                    \\\"涨跌幅\\\": round(change, 2),\\n                }\\n            elif len(data) == 1:\\n                price = float(data['Close'].iloc[-1])\\n                result[name] = {\\\"价格\\\": round(price, 2), \\\"前收\\\": \\\"-\\\", \\\"涨跌幅\\\": \\\"-\\\"}\\n            else:\\n                result[name] = {\\\"价格\\\": \\\"-\\\", \\\"前收\\\": \\\"-\\\", \\\"涨跌幅\\\": \\\"-\\\", \\\"error\\\": \\\"无数据\\\"}\\n        except Exception as e:\\n            result[name] = {\\\"价格\\\": \\\"-\\\", \\\"前收\\\": \\\"-\\\", \\\"涨跌幅\\\": \\\"-\\\", \\\"error\\\": str(e)}\\n\\n    return result\\n\\n\\ndef analyze_global_market(global_data):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"基于指数表现给出保守、证据驱动的全球市场判断\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    us_names = [\\\"道琼斯\\\", \\\"标普500\\\", \\\"纳斯达克\\\"]\\n    hk_names = [\\\"恒生指数\\\"]\\n\\n    us_changes = [global_data.get(name, {}).get(\\\"涨跌幅\\\") for name in us_names]\\n    us_changes = [x for x in us_changes if isinstance(x, (int, float))]\\n    hk_changes = [global_data.get(name, {}).get(\\\"涨跌幅\\\") for name in hk_names]\\n    hk_changes = [x for x in hk_changes if isinstance(x, (int, float))]\\n\\n    evidence = []\\n    if us_changes:\\n        us_avg = sum(us_changes) / len(us_changes)\\n        us_up = sum(1 for x in us_changes if x > 0)\\n        evidence.append(f\\\"美股三大指数 {us_up}/3 收涨，平均涨幅 {us_avg:+.2f}%\\\")\\n    else:\\n        us_avg = None\\n        us_up = 0\\n\\n    if hk_changes:\\n        evidence.append(f\\\"恒生指数 {hk_changes[0]:+.2f}%\\\")\\n\\n    if us_avg is None:\\n        summary = \\\"海外市场数据不足，暂不下方向性结论\\\"\\n        tone = \\\"中性\\\"\\n    elif us_up == 3 and us_avg >= 0.80:\\n        summary = \\\"隔夜海外市场明显走强，风险偏好修复较为清晰\\\"\\n        tone = \\\"偏强\\\"\\n    elif us_up == 3 and us_avg >= 0.20:\\n        summary = \\\"隔夜海外市场小幅修复，但力度一般，宜表述为偏稳或弱修复\\\"\\n        tone = \\\"偏稳\\\"\\n    elif us_up >= 2 and us_avg > -0.20:\\n        summary = \\\"隔夜海外市场分化震荡，未形成明确 risk-on / risk-off 信号\\\"\\n        tone = \\\"中性\\\"\\n    elif us_avg <= -0.50:\\n        summary = \\\"隔夜海外市场整体偏弱，风险偏好回落\\\"\\n        tone = \\\"偏弱\\\"\\n    else:\\n        summary = \\\"隔夜海外市场略偏弱，但暂无单边走弱共识\\\"\\n        tone = \\\"偏弱\\\"\\n\\n    caveat = \\\"仅依据主要指数涨跌判断；若需推导风格偏好，还应结合黄金、美元、美债收益率及成长/防御板块相对强弱。\\\"\\n\\n    return {\\n        \\\"结论\\\": summary,\\n        \\\"口径\\\": tone,\\n        \\\"依据\\\": evidence,\\n        \\\"提示\\\": caveat,\\n    }\\n\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":42002,"output":2311,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44313,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776387790682,"responseId":"resp_06c3af14b50a39800169e186d009b0819ba31a39f1a8529caa"}}
