{"type":"message","id":"87234c8c","parentId":"29989d3a","timestamp":"2026-04-17T01:26:27.485Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-17 09:21:18 GMT+8] ✅ 每日 A股 Overlay 任务执行完成。\nSystem: \nSystem: **执行摘要：**\nSystem: - 持仓价格补全：23 只（成功）\nSystem: - 候选池解释：跳过（未找到候选池文件）\nSystem: - 持仓风险观察：完成\nSystem: - 综合研判生成：成功，8 只候选，4 只持仓需关注\nSystem: \nSystem: **飞书消息已发送**（messageId: om_x100b512cfea008acb2cfd5c10633f82），内容包括：\nSystem: - 市场状态：risk_off\nSystem: - 候选池 8 只，Top 3（巨力索具/中超控股/神剑股份）\nSystem: - 持仓关注 4 只（REDUCE × 2，EXIT × 2）\nSystem: - 免责条款\nSystem: [2026-04-17 09:25:59 GMT+8] FAILED_CLOSED\nSystem: Runner JSON: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/web_source_fusion_daily_latest.json\nSystem: Reason: stale_web_source_latest (ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.json 生成于 2026-04-14 10:55:00，已超过 24 小时阈值)\nSystem: [2026-04-17 09:26:23 GMT+8] Feishu[coding-agent] DM | 张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae) [msg:om_x100b512c8d2a74b0c3839a91078629a, reply_to:om_x100b512c8cbbeca8b20e970dc091d2e]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b512c8d2a74b0c3839a91078629a\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-17 09:26 GMT+8\",\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"body\": \"[message_id=om_x100b512c8cbbeca8b20e970dc091d2e] FAILED_CLOSED\\nRunner JSON: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/web_source_fusion_daily_latest.json\\nReason: stale_web_source_latest (ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.json 生成于 2026-04-14 10:55:00，已超过 24 小时阈值)\"\n}\n```\n\nwhy failed"}],"timestamp":1776389187481}}
