 if it’s relevant. I could include lines from the file or just the path since it's more conversational. It might help to mention the exact times checked. The user wanted to know about the failure, so I could suggest refreshing holdings, but I’ll be careful with external actions. It’s a bit strange how the source and error don’t match up.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Exploring Freshness Gate Issues**\\n\\nThe freshness gate relies on the filename/path and generated_at metadata rather than checking if the content source was local_ths_app, which is why it was rejected. It might be worth mentioning this oddity regarding the stale_web_source_latest and ths_web_selected_holdings_latest coming from local_ths_app. If local fallback is expected, maybe the pipeline isn't respecting that or there's a naming issue. Since the user just wants to know why it failed, I can clarify that it wasn’t due to a data analysis error but an intentional freshness block.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 不是算法跑崩了，是**被新鲜度门禁主动拦下了**。\n\n我刚看了生成结果，失败原因写得很直接：\n\n- 检查时间：`2026-04-17 09:25:32`\n- 输入文件：`research/reports/ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.json`\n- 这个文件的 `generated_at`：`2026-04-14 10:55:00`\n- 阈值：`24 小时`\n\n所以它判定为：\n\n`stale_web_source_latest`\n\n也就是：**持仓源太旧，超过 24 小时，不允许继续生成/覆盖 web fusion 结果。**\n\n这属于**故意 fail-closed**，不是异常崩溃。  \n逻辑大概是：宁可不出结果，也不拿 3 天前的持仓去给你今天的判断，避免把旧仓位当真仓位。\n\n还有一个容易混淆的点：\n\n- 09:21 那个“每日 A股 Overlay 任务执行完成”是**另一条链路**，所以它能成功\n- 09:25 这个失败的是 **web_source_fusion** 这条链路，它**专门依赖**  \n  `ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.json`\n- 这条链路要求持仓文件必须是近 24 小时内更新的，所以被拦了\n\n我还顺手看了它的 meta，里面写的是：\n\n- `source: local_ths_app`\n- `generated_at: 2026-04-14 10:55:00`\n\n说明现在这个“latest”文件虽然叫 `ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.json`，但实际内容是**4 月 14 日从本地同花顺账本同步出来的旧快照**。  \n**问题本质不是文件丢了，而是文件太旧。**\n\n一句话版：\n\n**why failed = 因为它发现你用于 fusion 的持仓快照已经过期 3 天了，所以按安全策略拒绝继续。**\n\n如果你要，我下一步可以直接帮你做两件事里的一件：\n\n1. **刷新这份 selected holdings**，让任务恢复通过  \n2. **把这条链路改成更稳的降级策略**：网页源过期时，明确退回本地 ledger，而不是直接 FAILED_CLOSED\n\n我个人建议做第 2 个，比较不容易再复发。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06c3af14b50a39800169e18c897498819b8809103b091addd1\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":54906,"output":1060,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55966,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776389242047,"responseId":"resp_06c3af14b50a39800169e18c7bf96c819b93a28a2ea99e5e4a"}}
