{"type":"message","id":"0a919882","parentId":"02641f99","timestamp":"2026-04-17T02:34:49.058Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Examining THS market fetcher**\n\nLet's examine the `ths_market_fetcher.py` file to understand how THS Level2 is configured."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_GMI9nLJHFB0gT1RqFG4gehTo","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis_upgrade_preview/data_provider/ths_market_fetcher.py","offset":1,"limit":100}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":399,"output":141,"cacheRead":77824,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78364,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776393283208,"responseId":"0e481206-61b5-498d-b6e5-4a95126a42a5"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c1e881bc","parentId":"0a919882","timestamp":"2026-04-17T02:34:49.091Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_GMI9nLJHFB0gT1RqFG4gehTo","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\n\"\"\"\n===================================\nThsMarketFetcher - 同花顺 Level2 数据源 (Priority 0)\n===================================\n\n数据来源：thsdata SDK（seablue1985 账号，MAC绑定）\n特点：\n- Level2 超级盘口（52字段，10档委买卖盘，逐笔成交方向）\n- 大单流向（big_order_flow）\n- 委托订单簿（order_book_bid/ask）\n- 盘中实时报价，优先级最高\n\n接入方式：\n- THS格式代码: USZA000001 (深A), USHA600519 (沪A), USBA920xxx (北交所)\n\n防封禁策略：\n1. 每次连接后复用 Quote 实例，避免频繁新建\n2. buffer_size=10MB 接收 Level2 数据\n3. 异常时由 DataFetcherManager 自动切换到下一个数据源\n\n股票名称查找（thsdata Level2 tick 接口不返回股票名称，用本地表兜底）\n\"\"\"\n\n# 股票名称映射表（用于 Level2 tick 数据名称缺失时兜底）\ntry:\n    from src.data.stock_mapping import STOCK_NAME_MAP as _STOCK_NAME_MAP\nexcept Exception:\n    _STOCK_NAME_MAP = {}\n\nimport logging\nimport math\nimport time\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass, field\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom typing import Any, Dict, List, Optional, Tuple\n\nimport pandas as pd\n\nfrom src.config import get_config\nfrom .base import BaseFetcher, DataFetchError, RateLimitError, normalize_stock_code\nfrom .realtime_types import (\n    UnifiedRealtimeQuote,\n    RealtimeSource,\n    get_realtime_circuit_breaker,\n    safe_float,\n    safe_int,\n)\n\nlogger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n\n# THS 账号凭证\nWORKSPACE = \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\"\nCREDS_PATH = f\"{WORKSPACE}/config/thsdata_credentials.json\"\n\n# 全局 THS 连接实例（进程内复用）\n_ths_quote_cache: Optional[Any] = None\n_ths_cache_time: float = 0.0\n_THS_CACHE_TTL: float = 300.0  # 5分钟内复用连接\n\n\ndef _load_credentials() -> Dict[str, str]:\n    import json\n    with open(CREDS_PATH, encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n        return json.load(f)\n\n\ndef _get_ths_quote():\n    \"\"\"获取或创建 THS 连接（带缓存）\"\"\"\n    global _ths_quote_cache, _ths_cache_time\n    now = time.monotonic()\n    if _ths_quote_cache is not None and (now - _ths_cache_time) < _THS_CACHE_TTL:\n        return _ths_quote_cache\n    from thsdata import Quote\n    creds = _load_credentials()\n    q = Quote(ops={\n        \"username\": creds[\"username\"],\n        \"password\": creds[\"password\"],\n        \"mac\":      creds[\"mac\"],\n    })\n    q.connect()\n    logger.info(f\"[ThsMarketFetcher] THS connected: {creds['username']}\")\n    _ths_quote_cache = q\n    _ths_cache_time = now\n    return q\n\n\n# =============================================================================\n# 代码格式转换\n# =============================================================================\ndef ts_code_to_ths(ts_code: str) -> str:\n    \"\"\"任意股票代码格式 → THS格式 (USZA000001 / USHA600519 / USBA920xxx)\n\n    支持格式：\n    - 标准 ts_code: 000001.SZ, 600519.SH, 920xxx.BJ\n    - TDX格式: SZ000001, SH600519 (前缀大写)\n    - 纯数字: 000001, 600519 (自动推断市场)\n    \"\"\"\n\n[311 more lines in file. Use offset=101 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776393289081}}
