{"type":"message","id":"7e490036","parentId":"f2ec948b","timestamp":"2026-04-17T02:47:06.941Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_6CwCeuQOcYyDsNa3bzJZKnuN","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"Tongdaxin (同花顺) broker adapter.\n\nReal-trade adapter for Tongdaxin / iFinD API.\nSince Tongdaxin does NOT expose a public HTTP trading API, this adapter\nimplements a **manual confirmation queue** pattern:\n\n  - query_position() / query_account()  → read local holdings snapshot\n    (produced by scripts/sync_ths_exports.py or the ths_local_holdings skill)\n  - submit_order()                      → write order to orders/manual_confirm/\n    for human review and execution\n\nFor fully automated trading, switch to XtQuantBroker (迅投 QMT) which is\navailable on Linux/macOS, or use a broker with a supported REST API.\n\n---\n接入说明（同花顺官方 API 现状）：\n\n  同花顺官方 iFinD API（ifindapi）仅支持 Windows COM，Linux/macOS 无法使用。\n  如需真实下单，推荐以下方案：\n\n  1. 迅投 QMT（XtQuant）：支持华泰、招商、中信等主流券商，Linux/macOS 可用\n     → 使用 XtQuantBroker\n  2. 券商自营 REST API（如中信证券、华泰证券）\n     → 需联系券商开通量化权限\n  3. 聚合 API（如米筐、掘金量化）\n     → 需单独开户\n\n  本文件中的实现仅供参考，不进行真实下单。\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nfrom .broker_base import (\n    AccountInfo,\n    BrokerAdapter,\n    OrderResult,\n    Position,\n    register_broker,\n)\n\n\n@register_broker(\"tongdaxin\")\nclass TongdaxinBroker(BrokerAdapter):\n    \"\"\"同花顺券商适配器（人工确认队列模式）\n\n    Parameters\n\n[179 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776394026925}}
