"6\", \"9\")) else \"SZ\"\n        return f\"{raw}.{market}\"\n    return raw\n\n\ndef to_float(value: Any, default: float = np.nan) -> float:\n    try:\n        return float(value)\n    except Exception:\n        return default\n\n\ndef to_int(value: Any, default: int = 0) -> int:\n    try:\n        return int(float(value))\n    except Exception:\n        return default\n\n\ndef first_col(df: pd.DataFrame, candidates: list[str]) -> str | None:\n    for c in candidates:\n        if c in df.columns:\n            return c\n    for c in candidates:\n        c_lower = c.lower()\n        for real in df.columns:\n            if str(real).strip().lower() == c_lower:\n                return real\n    return None\n\n\ndef safe_read_table(path: Path) -> pd.DataFrame:\n    suffix = path.suffix.lower()\n    if suffix == \".csv\":\n        for enc in (\"utf-8-sig\", \"gb18030\", \"utf-8\"):\n            try:\n                return pd.read_csv(path, encoding=enc)\n            except Exception:\n                continue\n        return pd.DataFrame()\n    if suffix in {\".xls\", \".xlsx\"}:\n        try:\n            return pd.read_excel(path)\n        except Exception:\n\n[233 more lines in file. Use offset=101 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776394047911}}
{"type":"message","id":"02284828","parentId":"1aacc8f1","timestamp":"2026-04-17T02:47:55.271Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Understanding the issue**\n\nNow I understand the issue better. The system has multiple ways to get holdings data:\n1. **Local THS app database** (via `sync_ths_app_data.py`) - reads local SQLite files\n2. **THS export files** (via `sync_ths_exports.py`) - reads exported CSV/Excel files\n3. **THS Level2 interface** (via `thsdata_realtime.py`) - for real-time quotes, not holdings\n4. **Web API** (via `ths-local-holdings` skill) - for web-based holdings\n\nThe `ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.json` file is generated by the `ths-local-holdings` skill, which tries to get holdings from the web API first, then falls back to local app data.\n\nThe user's request \"数据源用我的同花顺level2接口\" might mean they want to use the THS Level2 interface **for holdings data**, not just for real-time quotes. But the THS Level2 interface (`thsdata`) is primarily for real-time market data, not for account holdings.\n\nHowever, there might be a way to get holdings through the THS Level2 interface. Let me check if the `thsdata` SDK has account/position query capabilities.\n\nActually, looking back at the user's credentials, they provided the same credentials that are already in use. This suggests they might be confirming that these are indeed their credentials. The real issue might be that the THS Level2 interface isn't being used for the web source fusion pipeline.\n\nLet me respond to clarify and suggest a solution."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_p5mdT4YpnziOyizl7ltCECan","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"[[reply_to_current]] 我核对了一下：\n\n1. **当前配置**已经用的是 `seablue1985`（就是你刚发的这个）\n2. **MAC地址** `1c:f6:4c:5f:af:e5` 也匹配本机\n\n所以**账号层面已经是你自己的**，不需要改。\n\n---\n\n**问题在于**：`web_source_fusion` 这条链路用的不是 Level2 接口，而是**本地同花顺账本快照**（`local_ths_app`）。\n\n证据：`ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.meta.json` 里写的是：\n```json\n{\n  \"source\": \"local_ths_app\",\n  \"generated_at\": \"2026-04-14 10:55:00\"\n}\n```\n\n这说明它 4 月 14 日从本地账本导出了一次，之后**再也没更新过**。\n\n---\n\n**你要我改的“设置”具体是哪个？**\n\n选项 A：**把 web source fusion 的源改成 Level2 接口**\n- 需要确认 thsdata SDK 是否支持查询账户持仓（不只是行情）\n- 如果支持，我改 `ths-local-holdings` 技能，让它优先走 Level2 接口查持仓\n\n选项 B：**只是刷新一下当前快照**\n- 我直接跑一次 `sync_ths_app_data.py` 或 `sync_ths_exports.py`，生成新的 `ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.json`\n- 这样就能过 24 小时新鲜度检查\n\n选项 C：**把新鲜度阈值从 24 小时放宽**\n- 比如改成 72 小时，这样 4 月 14 日的快照还能用\n- 但这是掩耳盗铃，不推荐\n\n**我建议先做 B**（刷新快照），因为最直接。如果你确认 thsdata 能查持仓，我们再做 A。"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":856,"output":808,"cacheRead":84352,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86016,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776394047924,"responseId":"3ebd7a2e-6c66-4f0e-893a-f3d8465fe13a"}}
