{"type":"message","id":"242e6206","parentId":"a1b1d8ef","timestamp":"2026-04-17T02:51:45.112Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! The file is now fresh (only 0.01 hours old, which is less than a minute).\n\nNow let me update the user on what I've done and suggest they try running the web source fusion pipeline again."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ANlMS9wIyYR0Sz69wKWywZDv","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"[[reply_to_current]] **已刷新持仓快照**\n\n执行步骤：\n1. 运行 `sync_ths_app_data.py` → 扫描到 45 条持仓（来自 3 个本地账本文件）\n2. 过滤出 41 只 A 股，更新 `ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.json/csv/meta.json`\n3. 新时间戳：`2026-04-17 10:50:59`（新鲜度 ✅）\n\n**当前状态：**\n- 持仓源：`local_ths_app`（本地同花顺账本）\n- 持仓数：41 只 A 股\n- 文件年龄：≈ 0.01 小时（远小于 24 小时阈值）\n\n**下一步：**\n现在 `web_source_fusion` 应该能过新鲜度检查了。  \n你可以：\n- 手动触发一次 web fusion 任务\n- 或者等下次定时执行（如果配置了 cron）\n\n**关于“用 Level2 接口”的澄清：**\n你发的账号/MAC 和当前配置一致，说明 Level2 行情接口**已经在用**（实时报价优先级最高）。  \n但持仓同步走的是另一条路（本地账本 → CSV → JSON）。\n\n如果**确实需要**让持仓也走 Level2 接口（假设 thsdata SDK 支持查账户持仓），我可以改 `ths-local-holdings` 技能。  \n不过从实际效果看，本地账本刷新已经解决了新鲜度问题。\n\n先试试现在能不能跑通？"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":110,"output":429,"cacheRead":92288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92827,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776394289484,"responseId":"5a4b1558-9ff3-4ef8-a6a7-21430c236034"}}
