{"type":"message","id":"0e753efd","parentId":"437be698","timestamp":"2026-04-17T02:57:44.250Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Found it! There's a `probe_ths_level2` function for health checks. Let me look at this function."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_s4FdSqQYJwLvu7oooUbwvJfO","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/thsdata_realtime.py","offset":259,"limit":100}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":135,"output":129,"cacheRead":122304,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122568,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776394657427,"responseId":"8922db64-6d5e-4c67-a71a-d7b1f942b4fa"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e766e93a","parentId":"0e753efd","timestamp":"2026-04-17T02:57:44.289Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_s4FdSqQYJwLvu7oooUbwvJfO","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 健康探针（用于 investment_research_data_source_health）\n# =============================================================================\ndef probe_ths_level2(tickers: list[str]) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    \"\"\"对指定 ticker 列表做 thsdata Level2 健康探针\"\"\"\n    results = []\n    for ts_code in tickers:\n        started = time.perf_counter()\n        quote = get_realtime_quote(ts_code)\n        elapsed_ms = round((time.perf_counter() - started) * 1000, 1)\n        results.append({\n            \"ts_code\": ts_code,\n            \"ths_code\": quote.ths_code,\n            \"status\": quote.status,\n            \"source\": quote.source,\n            \"price\": quote.price,\n            \"change_pct\": quote.change_pct,\n            \"bid1\": quote.bid1,\n            \"ask1\": quote.ask1,\n            \"bid_vol1\": quote.bid_vol1,\n            \"ask_vol1\": quote.ask_vol1,\n            \"latency_ms\": elapsed_ms,\n            \"error\": quote.error,\n        })\n\n    ok = [r for r in results if r[\"status\"] == \"ok\"]\n    fallbacks = [r for r in results if r[\"status\"] == \"fallback\"]\n    failed = [r for r in results if r[\"status\"] == \"failed\"]\n\n    return {\n        \"available\": len(ok) > 0,\n        \"checked\": len(results),\n        \"ok_count\": len(ok),\n        \"fallback_count\": len(fallbacks),\n        \"failed_count\": len(failed),\n        \"results\": results,\n    }\n\n\n# =============================================================================\n# CLI\n# =============================================================================\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    import sys\n    if len(sys.argv) < 2:\n        print(\"Usage: python3 thsdata_realtime.py <ts_code>\")\n        print(\"Example: python3 thsdata_realtime.py 000001.SZ\")\n        sys.exit(1)\n\n    ts_code = sys.argv[1].strip()\n    print(f\"=== THS Level2 Quote: {ts_code} ===\")\n    quote = get_realtime_quote(ts_code)\n    print(f\"ths_code: {quote.ths_code}\")\n    print(f\"price:    {quote.price}\")\n    print(f\"change%:  {quote.change_pct}%\")\n    print(f\"volume:   {quote.volume}\")\n    print(f\"bid:      {quote.bid1} x {quote.bid_vol1}\")\n    print(f\"ask:      {quote.ask1} x {quote.ask_vol1}\")\n    print(f\"status:   {quote.status}\")\n    if quote.error:\n        print(f\"error:    {quote.error}\")\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776394664271}}
{"type":"message","id":"5581b4c7","parentId":"e766e93a","timestamp":"2026-04-17T02:57:54.755Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I need to find where this health probe is called and what might be causing the \"数据源健康警戒\" (data source health alert). Let me search for where `probe_ths_level2` is called or where data source health is checked."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Y7QxpQerU9amUSr8Ru18rI7X","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -r \"probe_ths_level2\\|investment_research_data_source_health\" /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system --include=\"*.py\" --include=\"*.json\" --include=\"*.yaml\" --include=\"*.yml\" 2>/dev/null | head -n 50","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent","timeout":20}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":613,"output":218,"cacheRead":122560,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123391,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776394664292,"responseId":"2c1b4bc1-8dc8-4444-b002-8152ae98e50b"}}
