{"type":"message","id":"faf2d261","parentId":"1eabd99d","timestamp":"2026-04-17T02:58:33.796Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_tv9Kcf7JDBxarkX0ResecD9x","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# ============================================\n# 量化系统定时任务配置\n# 生成时间: 2026-04-15 14:25:49\n# 项目: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\n# ============================================\n\n# 更新可靠持仓数据 (交易日开盘后和盘中)\n30 9 * * * cd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system && ./cron/update_reliable_holdings.sh >> ./logs/cron_update_holdings.log 2>&1\n30 14 * * * cd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system && ./cron/update_reliable_holdings.sh >> ./logs/cron_update_holdings.log 2>&1\n\n# 检查数据新鲜度 (交易日三个时间点)\n0 10 * * * cd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system && ./cron/check_data_freshness.sh >> ./logs/cron_check_freshness.log 2>&1\n0 13 * * * cd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system && ./cron/check_data_freshness.sh >> ./logs/cron_check_freshness.log 2>&1\n0 16 * * * cd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system && ./cron/check_data_freshness.sh >> ./logs/cron_check_freshness.log 2>&1\n\n# ============================================\n# 说明:\n# 1. 所有任务都在项目目录下运行\n# 2. 日志输出到 logs/ 目录\n# 3. 自动清理7天前的日志\n# ============================================\n\n# 周末清理日志 (每周日凌晨)\n0 2 * * 0 find /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/logs -name \"cron_*.log\" -mtime +7 -delete\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776394713784}}
{"type":"message","id":"1a03ea78","parentId":"faf2d261","timestamp":"2026-04-17T02:58:57.756Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me think about what the user is asking. They're seeing two alerts:\n1. **审计未通过** (audit_status=ALERT) - From the audit file, this is because of `\"aggressive:dated_artifact_tag_mismatch\"` (aggressive profile has artifacts with mismatched date tags)\n2. **数据源健康警戒** (data source health degraded, health_probe downgraded) - This might be related to THS Level2 data source health probe\n\nThe user is asking \"为什么审计未通过？数据源不是正在接通吗？\" (Why did the audit fail? Isn't the data source connected?)\n\nLet me respond with what I've found."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_3sjhwXuIsFrMyv7IDKJQGg5N","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"[[reply_to_current]] 两个问题分开看：\n\n### 1. 审计未通过 (audit_status=ALERT)\n**原因**：`aggressive:dated_artifact_tag_mismatch`\n\naggressive 模拟盘的几个文件日期标签不一致：\n- `journal`: 20260413（4月13日）\n- `orders`/`tickets`/`order_plan`: 20260415（4月15日）\n\n审计规则要求同一 profile 的所有 artifacts 必须是同一天生成的，否则视为“口径不一致”，触发 ALERT。\n\n**这不是数据源问题**，是文件生成时间没对齐。  \n**修复**：重新生成 aggressive profile 的 journal 文件（或把其他文件回滚到 4月13日）。\n\n---\n\n### 2. 数据源健康警戒 (health_probe 降级)\n这个可能和 THS Level2 健康探针有关。  \n系统里有个 `probe_ths_level2()` 函数，会测试几个 ticker 的实时行情获取能力。\n\n**可能的原因**：\n- THS Level2 连接超时/失败\n- 返回了 fallback 数据（非 Level2 源）\n- 探针 ticker 列表里某些代码拿不到行情\n\n**检查方法**：跑一次健康探针\n```bash\ncd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/thsdata_realtime.py 000001.SZ\n```\n\n如果返回 `status: \"ok\"` 且 `source: \"ths_level2\"`，说明 Level2 接口正常。  \n如果 `status: \"fallback\"` 或 `\"failed\"`，才是数据源降级。\n\n---\n\n**你的问题“数据源不是正在接通吗？”**  \n- 持仓同步的**数据源**（本地同花顺账本）刚才已经刷新成功（41只A股）\n- 实时行情的**数据源**（THS Level2）需要单独探针验证\n- 审计失败的**原因**是文件日期不一致，不是数据源不通\n\n要我帮你：\n1. **修复审计**（对齐 aggressive profile 文件日期）\n2. **检查 Level2 健康**（跑探针看具体降级原因）\n\n选一个先做？"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":567,"output":691,"cacheRead":124224,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125482,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776394713800,"responseId":"dc7f5653-b234-47ed-8ae4-3406bc2869f6"}}
