ripts/sync_ths_exports.py or the ths_local_holdings skill)\n  - submit_order()                      → write order to orders/manual_confirm/\n    for human review and execution\n\nFor fully automated trading, switch to XtQuantBroker (迅投 QMT) which is\navailable on Linux/macOS, or use a broker with a supporte...\n- Assistant: **Looking for sync scripts**\n\nLet me search for sync scripts more broadly.\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/sync_ths_app_data.py\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/sync_ths_exports.py\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/sync_sector_board_data.py\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/sync_broker_api_data.py\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/backups_20260415/scripts_backup/sync_ths_app_data.py\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/wo...\n- Assistant: **Examining THS sync scripts**\n\nLet me check `sync_ths_app_data.py` and `sync_ths_exports.py` to understand how holdings are synced.\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (read): from __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nimport hashlib\nimport json\nimport re\nimport sqlite3\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nimport numpy as np\nimport pandas as pd\n\nPROJECT_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\nREPORT_DIR = PROJECT_ROOT / \"research\" / \"reports\"\nCONFIG_DIR = PROJECT_ROOT / \"config\"\nPORTFOLIO_PATH = CONFIG_DIR / \"portfolio_positions.csv\"\n\nDB_SUFFIX = {\".db\", \".sqlite\", \".sqlite3\"}\n\nCODE_COLS = [\"ts_code\", \"symbol\", \"code\", \"stock_code\", \"security_code\", \"sec_code\", \"fund_code\", \"stockid\", \"stk_code\"]\nNAME_COLS = [\"na...\n- Assistant: **Checking sync_ths_exports.py**\n\nLet me also check `sync_