{"type":"message","id":"0603d19c","parentId":"8a21c7b7","timestamp":"2026-04-17T03:01:51.600Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I can see that `ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.json` is used by many reports. The note in `ths_local_holdings_selection.json` says it's the \"primary source\". \n\nNow I need to understand how this file is generated. Based on earlier investigation, it seems to be generated by the `ths-local-holdings` skill. Let me check if there's a script or skill that generates this file."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_S5JDhZnYFk5yY5H51An1P8bY","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /Users/ling/.openclaw/skills -name \"*ths*holdings*\" -o -name \"*holdings*ths*\" 2>/dev/null | head -n 50","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent","timeout":20}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":2397,"output":222,"cacheRead":73856,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76475,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776394901392,"responseId":"5555f41f-637b-48ce-87f4-429cd166bd5d"}}
