{"type":"message","id":"e68f705a","parentId":"eb210b07","timestamp":"2026-04-17T03:01:57.129Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Found it! The `ths-local-holdings` skill. Let me check its script."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_G35ZuH9BSXJWGh99Deu3kzDk","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/ths_local_holdings.py","offset":1,"limit":100}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":140,"output":117,"cacheRead":76416,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76673,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776394911743,"responseId":"37f38405-fad0-4b25-b386-ccabd4471904"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ecfad106","parentId":"e68f705a","timestamp":"2026-04-17T03:01:57.181Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_G35ZuH9BSXJWGh99Deu3kzDk","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nimport csv\nimport json\nimport sys\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\n\nDEFAULT_ROOTS = [\n    Path.home() / \"Library\" / \"Containers\" / \"cn.com.10jqka.macstockPro\" / \"Data\",\n    Path.home() / \"Library\" / \"Containers\" / \"cn.com.10jqka.ixcs\" / \"Data\",\n    Path.home() / \"Library\" / \"Group Containers\" / \"group.cn.com.10jqka.ixcs\",\n]\n\n\n@dataclass\nclass Holding:\n    symbol: str\n    name: str\n    quantity: int\n    cost_price: float | None\n    asset_type: str\n    source_path: str\n    ledger_ids: list[str]\n\n\ndef normalize_code(value: Any) -> str:\n    raw = str(value or \"\").strip().upper()\n    if not raw or raw == \"NAN\":\n        return \"\"\n    if raw.endswith(\".XSHG\"):\n        return raw.replace(\".XSHG\", \".SH\")\n    if raw.endswith(\".XSHE\"):\n        return raw.replace(\".XSHE\", \".SZ\")\n    if raw.endswith((\".SH\", \".SZ\", \".HK\")):\n        return raw\n    if raw.startswith(\"SH\") and len(raw) >= 8:\n        return f\"{raw[2:8]}.SH\"\n    if raw.startswith(\"SZ\") and len(raw) >= 8:\n        return f\"{raw[2:8]}.SZ\"\n    if raw.isdigit() and len(raw) == 6:\n        market = \"SH\" if raw.startswith((\"5\", \"6\", \"9\")) else \"SZ\"\n        return f\"{raw}.{market}\"\n    if raw.isdigit() and len(raw) == 5:\n        return f\"{raw}.HK\"\n    return raw\n\n\ndef infer_asset_type(symbol: str) -> str:\n    code = symbol.split(\".\")[0]\n    if code.startswith((\"5\", \"1\", \"15\")):\n        return \"fund\"\n    return \"stock\"\n\n\ndef normalize_side(value: Any) -> str:\n    text = str(value or \"\").strip().upper()\n    if any(k in text for k in [\"买\", \"BUY\", \"B\", \"证券买入\", \"申购\"]):\n        return \"BUY\"\n    if any(k in text for k in [\"卖\", \"SELL\", \"S\", \"证券卖出\", \"赎回\"]):\n        return \"SELL\"\n    return text\n\n\ndef discover_roots(extra_roots: list[str] | None = None) -> list[Path]:\n    roots = list(DEFAULT_ROOTS)\n    containers_root = Path.home() / \"Library\" / \"Containers\"\n    if containers_root.exists():\n        for d in containers_root.iterdir():\n            if not d.is_dir():\n                continue\n            candidate = d / \"Data\" / \"Documents\" / \"cn.com.10jqka.ixcs\"\n            if candidate.exists():\n                roots.append(d / \"Data\")\n    if extra_roots:\n        roots.extend(Path(x).expanduser().resolve() for x in extra_roots)\n\n    uniq: list[Path] = []\n    seen: set[Path] = set()\n    for p in roots:\n        p = p.resolve()\n        if p in seen:\n            continue\n        seen.add(p)\n        uniq.append(p)\n    return uniq\n\n\ndef list_ledger_files(roots: list[Path]) -> list[Path]:\n    files: list[Path] = []\n    for root in roots:\n        if not root.exists():\n            continue\n        try:\n            files.extend(root.rglob(\"XcsLscjDataFile_*\"))\n        except Exception:\n\n[290 more lines in file. Use offset=101 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776394917172}}
{"type":"message","id":"98a5926a","parentId":"ecfad106","timestamp":"2026-04-17T03:02:12.509Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This script reads local THS app data files. This is the current source (`local_ths_app`). The user wants to change this to use THS Level2 interface instead.\n\nHowever, there's a fundamental issue: **THS Level2 interface is for real-time quotes, not for fetching holdings/portfolio data**. The Level2 interface gives you market data (prices, volumes, bids/asks), not account holdings.\n\nTo get holdings data from THS, you would need:\n1. **THS trading API** (if available) - to query account positions\n2. **THS web API** (if available) - to query holdings via web interface\n3. **Local THS app database** (what we're currently using) - reads local files\n4. **Exported files** (CSV/Excel) - manual exports\n\nThe user might be confusing:\n- **THS Level2 for real-time quotes** (already working for market data)\n- **THS holdings data source** (currently from local app, could be from web API)\n\nLet me check if there's a THS web API for holdings. Let me look for any web-based THS holdings scripts."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_HCNe0AorXfMwuvRbg8PLw1X7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system -name \"*.py\" -exec grep -l \"web.*holdings\\|holdings.*web\" {} \\; 2>/dev/null | head -n 50","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent","timeout":20}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":856,"output":391,"cacheRead":76672,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77919,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776394917183,"responseId":"7f933815-8ef0-4f9c-96f1-63ffc69d06a9"}}
