{"type":"message","id":"4c913f97","parentId":"e76fbf5b","timestamp":"2026-04-17T03:03:10.126Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_IoHa0IRYBRIyQcITiKJPtjsG","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nimport csv\nimport json\nimport re\nimport shutil\nimport subprocess\nimport sys\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass\nfrom datetime import date, datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nWORKSPACE = Path.home() / \".openclaw\" / \"workspace\"\nDEFAULT_OUTPUT_DIR = (\n    WORKSPACE / \"quant_projects\" / \"personal-a-share-research-system\" / \"research\" / \"reports\"\n)\nSTOCK_DAILY_DIR = WORKSPACE / \"skills\" / \"stock-daily-report\"\nSTOCK_DAILY_ENTRY = STOCK_DAILY_DIR / \"generate_report.py\"\nSTOCK_DAILY_CONFIG = STOCK_DAILY_DIR / \"config.json\"\nSTOCK_WATCHER_WATCHLIST = Path.home() / \".clawdbot\" / \"stock_watcher\" / \"watchlist.txt\"\nAKSHARE_STOCK_CLI = Path.home() / \".openclaw\" / \"skills\" / \"akshare-stock\" / \"scripts\" / \"stock_cli.py\"\nSTOCK_WATCHER_SUMMARY = (\n    Path.home() / \".openclaw\" / \"skills\" / \"stock-watcher\" / \"scripts\" / \"summarize_performance.py\"\n)\nAUTODISCOVER_PATTERNS: list[tuple[str, str]] = [\n    (\"ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.json\", \"ths_web_selected_holdings\"),\n    (\"ths_web_selected_holdings_*.json\", \"ths_web_selected_holdings\"),\n    (\"ths_web_holding_count_fix_*.json\", \"ths_web_holding_count_fix\"),\n    (\"ths_app_holdings_*.csv\", \"ths_app_holdings\"),\n]\nCODE_FIELD_CANDIDATES = [\n    \"code\",\n    \"symbol\",\n    \"ticker\",\n    \"stock_code\",\n    \"security_code\",\n    \"证券代码\",\n    \"股票代码\",\n    \"代码\",\n    \"证券\",\n]\n\n\nclass FusionReportError(RuntimeError):\n    def __init__(\n        self,\n        code: str,\n        message: str,\n        *,\n        details: dict[str, Any] | None = None,\n        exit_code: int = 2,\n    ) -> None:\n        super().__init__(message)\n        self.code = code\n        self.message = message\n        self.details = details or {}\n        self.exit_code = exit_code\n\n    def to_payload(self) -> dict[str, Any]:\n        return {\n            \"code\": self.code,\n            \"message\": self.message,\n            \"details\": self.details,\n            \"exit_code\": self.exit_code,\n        }\n\n\n@dataclass\nclass InputBundle:\n    source_kind: str\n    source_file: str\n    source_label: str\n    rows: list[dict[str, Any]]\n    all_codes: list[str]\n    a_share_codes: list[str]\n    non_a_codes: list[str]\n    invalid_rows: list[dict[str, Any]]\n    selected_a_share_codes: list[str]\n\n\n@dataclass\nclass RunArtifacts:\n    run_id: str\n    run_dir: Path\n    input_snapshot_json: Path\n    input_snapshot_csv: Path\n    report_md: Path\n    summary_json: Path\n    run_summary_txt: Path\n    legacy_report_md: Path\n    legacy_summary_json: Path\n    latest_report_md: Path\n    latest_summary_json: Path\n    latest_run_summary_txt: Path\n    latest_input_snapshot_json: Path\n    latest_input_snapshot_csv: Path\n\n\n[914 more lines in file. Use offset=101 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776394990119}}
{"type":"message","id":"72ad54cb","parentId":"4c913f97","timestamp":"2026-04-17T03:03:35.721Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This is the fusion report script. It uses `ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.json` as input. The user wants to change this source to use Level2 interface.\n\nHowever, I need to clarify: **THS Level2 interface doesn't provide holdings data**. It provides real-time market data. The holdings data comes from either:\n1. Local THS app database (current source)\n2. THS web interface (via web scraping)\n3. Manual exports\n\nIf the user wants \"more reliable\" or \"more real-time\" holdings data, they might want to:\n1. **Use THS web API** (if available) - more reliable than local app\n2. **Use THS trading API** (if available) - most accurate\n3. **Improve local app sync frequency** - what I just did\n\nGiven the confusion, let me ask for clarification and explain the options."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ycJxad9ZO5IfD9pzwblX41NG","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"[[reply_to_current]] **澄清需求：THS Level2 接口 ≠ 持仓数据源**\n\n**当前情况**：\n- `web_source_fusion` 的输入是 `ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.json`\n- 这个文件目前来自 `local_ths_app`（本地同花顺账本）\n- 我刚刷新了它（41只A股，2026-04-17 10:50:59）\n\n**关键区别**：\n1. **THS Level2 接口** → 实时行情（价格、买卖盘、成交量）\n2. **持仓数据源** → 账户持股列表（代码、数量、成本价）\n\nLevel2 **不提供**持仓数据，只提供行情数据。\n\n---\n\n**如果你想要的是**：\n✅ **用 Level2 实时行情计算持仓市值**（在 fusion report 里）\n→ 这个**已经实现**了：fusion report 会调用 `stock-daily-report`，后者会用 Level2 取最新价\n\n❌ **用 Level2 接口获取持仓列表**（替换本地账本）\n→ **技术上不可能**：Level2 API 没有 `get_holdings()` 方法\n\n---\n\n**可行的改进方向**：\n1. **提高本地账本刷新频率**（已做：从 4月14日 → 4月17日）\n2. **启用 THS 网页持仓同步**（如果网页接口还在工作）\n3. **对接 THS 交易 API**（如果有权限）\n\n**你的具体目标**：\nA. 让 fusion report 用 Level2 最新价（✓ 已支持）\nB. 让持仓数据源更可靠（需要明确：网页接口 vs 本地账本 vs 交易API）\nC. 其他？\n\n选 A 还是 B？"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":872,"output":620,"cacheRead":80512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82004,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776394990128,"responseId":"4fb0d356-11b7-41af-a8a0-fba7d9d7f6dd"}}
