{"type":"message","id":"551e7725","parentId":"cf6dc51d","timestamp":"2026-04-17T03:06:12.352Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-17 11:03:48 GMT+8] Feishu[coding-agent] DM | 张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae) [msg:om_x100b512e6c7d24acc2b534d06d55dcd]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b512e6c7d24acc2b534d06d55dcd\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-17 10:59 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\n我每天就忙于修复这个破破烂烂的量化系统，这个系统截至目前根本没有给我提供任何价值"}],"timestamp":1776395172346}}
{"type":"message","id":"7e4cb622","parentId":"551e7725","timestamp":"2026-04-17T03:06:34.611Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Understanding user frustration**\n\nThe user is expressing frustration with the quant system - they're spending time fixing it but feel it's not providing value. This is a deeper issue than just technical fixes.\n\nI need to address both the emotional frustration and the practical issues. The user wants the system to work reliably and provide value, not just be a maintenance burden.\n\nLet me respond empathetically and offer a practical approach."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_EvL81yY5VVpGXY5Ml9eOkylH","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"[[reply_to_current]] 我完全理解你的 frustration。花时间修修补补而不是用系统赚钱，这确实让人恼火。\n\n**现状诊断**：\n1. **系统过于复杂** - 多个数据源、审计规则、健康检查互相纠缠\n2. **维护负担重** - 每天要处理审计失败、数据源降级、文件过期\n3. **价值不明确** - 修好了也不知道能带来什么收益\n\n**根本问题**：\n你不是量化研究员，你是**投资者**。系统应该为你服务，而不是反过来。\n\n---\n\n**提议：简化到核心价值流**\n\n**第一步：停掉所有非核心链路**\n1. 关掉 `web_source_fusion`（它只是把持仓数据转一道手）\n2. 关掉 `daily_strategy_audit`（除非你要看模拟盘绩效）\n3. 只保留：\n   - 持仓同步（`sync_ths_app_data.py`）\n   - 早间报告（`generate_morning_news.py`）\n   - 实盘信号（如果有）\n\n**第二步：建立稳定基线**\n1. 持仓数据 → 每天开盘前自动刷新一次\n2. 早间报告 → 用最新持仓 + Level2 行情\n3. 去掉所有“新鲜度检查”、“健康探针”、“审计规则”\n\n**第三步：明确价值指标**\n- 系统应该告诉你：**今天该买什么、卖什么、持有什么**\n- 而不是：文件日期不一致、数据源降级、审计失败\n\n---\n\n**如果你同意，我可以：**\n1. 关掉 `web_source_fusion` 任务（它已经没用了）\n2. 简化持仓同步（每天 9:00 自动跑一次）\n3. 让早间报告直接读最新持仓 + Level2 行情\n4. 去掉所有让你分心的“系统健康”告警\n\n**目标**：你每天只看一份干净的早间报告 + 交易信号，不用管系统内部状态。\n\n这样行吗？"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":605,"output":561,"cacheRead":82048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83214,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776395172353,"responseId":"8abb42a4-baa1-4736-849b-fb79adc4d04f"}}
