{"type":"message","id":"1ef12c59","parentId":"9c7cdc09","timestamp":"2026-04-17T03:07:48.542Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-17 11:06:39 GMT+8] Feishu[coding-agent] DM | 张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae) [msg:om_x100b512e7525cc80b32d7c8a54d314e, reply_to:om_x100b512e7e485ca8b21be411adcc6c6]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b512e7525cc80b32d7c8a54d314e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-17 11:06 GMT+8\",\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"body\": \"[message_id=om_x100b512e7e485ca8b21be411adcc6c6] **澄清需求：THS Level2 接口 ≠ 持仓数据源**\\n**当前情况**：\\n- web_source_fusion 的输入是 ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.json\\n- 这个文件目前来自 local_ths_app（本地同花顺账本）\\n- 我刚刷新了它（41只A股，2026-04-17 10:50:59）\\n**关键区别**：\\n1. **THS Level2 接口** → 实时行情（价格、买卖盘、成交量）\\n2. **持仓数据源** → 账户持股列表（代码、数量、成本价）\\nLevel2 **不提供**持仓数据，只提供行情数据。\\n\\n---\\n\\n**如果你想要的是**：\\n✅ **用 Level2 实时行情计算持仓市值**（在 fusion report 里）\\n→ 这个**已经实现**了：fusion report 会调用 stock-daily-report，后者会用 Level2 取最新价\\n❌ **用 Level2 接口获取持仓列表**（替换本地账本）\\n→ **技术上不可能**：Level2 API 没有 get_holdings() 方法\\n\\n---\\n\\n**可行的改进方向**：\\n1. **提高本地账本刷新频率**（已做：从 4月14日 → 4月17日）\\n2. **启用 THS 网页持仓同步**（如果网页接口还在工作）\\n3. **对接 THS 交易 API**（如果有权限）\\n**你的具体目标**：\\nA. 让 fusion report 用 Level2 最新价（✓ 已支持）\\nB. 让持仓数据源更可靠（需要明确：网页接口 vs 本地账本 vs 交易API）\\nC. 其他？\\n选 A 还是 B？\"\n}\n```\n\n我现在还不需要量化系统实盘操作，你不用管我的实盘"}],"timestamp":1776395268537}}
{"type":"message","id":"5c8aedba","parentId":"1ef12c59","timestamp":"2026-04-17T03:08:08.196Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Understanding the real need**\n\nThe user is clarifying they don't need the quant system for live trading yet. They're frustrated with maintaining a complex system that's not providing value. \n\nThe core issue seems to be: they want reliable data (holdings + market data) for analysis/reporting, not for automated trading. The system is over-engineered for their current needs.\n\nLet me focus on what they actually need: reliable data sources for reporting/analysis, without all the complexity."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_x4gvKeFha8PfCp5oEKwTQ2Pz","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"[[reply_to_current]] 明白了。你不做实盘，那系统应该只做一件事：**给你可靠的持仓+行情数据，用于分析决策**。\n\n**当前问题根源**：\n系统设计成了“全自动交易引擎”，但你只需要“数据看板”。\n\n**简化方案**：\n\n### 1. 关掉所有交易相关链路\n- `web_source_fusion`（已失败）\n- `daily_strategy_audit`（审计失败）\n- `paper_profiles_*`（模拟盘）\n- `live_execution_*`（实盘信号）\n\n### 2. 只保留数据链路\n- **持仓同步**：`sync_ths_app_data.py` → 每天自动跑一次\n- **早间报告**：`generate_morning_news.py` → 用最新持仓 + Level2 行情\n- （可选）**个股分析**：`stock-daily-report` → 按需手动跑\n\n### 3. 去掉所有健康检查\n- 数据新鲜度检查（关掉）\n- 审计规则（关掉）\n- 健康探针（关掉）\n\n---\n\n**具体操作**：\n1. 我先把 `web_source_fusion` 标记为“已废弃”，不让它再失败告警\n2. 设置持仓同步每天 9:00 自动跑（稳定可靠）\n3. 让早间报告直接读同步后的持仓文件\n4. 所有“系统内部状态”告警全部静音\n\n**结果**：\n- 每天 9:30 收到一份干净的早间报告\n- 报告基于最新持仓 + Level2 实时行情\n- 没有审计失败、数据源降级等噪音\n\n**同意吗？我现在就执行第1步。**"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":1571,"output":526,"cacheRead":83264,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85361,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776395268543,"responseId":"499dd305-441b-49d6-a643-4f04609f1b9f"}}
