{"type":"message","id":"b042b3e1","parentId":"be9c6f7d","timestamp":"2026-04-17T03:20:05.968Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Addressing user concerns**\n\nThe user has two concerns:\n1. **\"不用同步我的实盘持仓！\"** (Don't sync my real holdings!) - Already addressed in the final configuration\n2. **\"实时计算会不会浪费很多token？\"** (Will real-time calculation waste a lot of tokens?) - Good question about cost efficiency\n\nThe user is concerned about the cost (tokens) of real-time calculations. This is a valid concern. Let me explain the trade-offs and provide options."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_DUkn3hMCE8Eu4UCQiCpq4SR7","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"[[reply_to_current]] **Token 消耗分析** 🔍\n\n### 当前配置（平衡方案）\n```\n9:20  早盘批量计算（一次）\n11:00 盘中检查（一次）\n13:00 盘中检查（一次）\n```\n**每天 3 次计算**，每次约 50-100K tokens（取决于股票数量）。\n\n### 实时计算方案（每5分钟）\n```\n9:00-15:00 每5分钟计算一次\n```\n**每天 ~72 次计算**，每次 50K tokens → **~3.6M tokens/天**（确实浪费）。\n\n### 优化建议\n\n**方案 A：事件驱动（推荐）**\n- 只在**市场有变化时**计算（大涨/大跌/突破）\n- 用技术指标触发（RSI超买超卖、突破均线等）\n- 最省 token，最智能\n\n**方案 B：关键时点**\n- 9:20（开盘前）\n- 10:30（早盘趋势确立）\n- 13:30（午盘趋势确立）\n- 14:30（尾盘机会）\n- **每天 4 次**，平衡实时性与成本\n\n**方案 C：纯批量**\n- 9:20 计算全天信号\n- 盘中不重新计算\n- **每天 1 次**，最省 token\n\n### 我的建议\n**用方案 B（关键时点）**：\n- 足够实时（4次/天）\n- 成本可控（~400K tokens/天）\n- 覆盖主要交易时段\n\n**调整后配置**：\n```\n9:20  早盘信号\n10:30 早盘趋势确认  \n13:30 午盘机会\n14:30 尾盘机会\n```\n\n**同意吗？我按方案 B 调整。**"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":1532,"output":548,"cacheRead":100352,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102432,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776395981092,"responseId":"50c87b88-d4eb-4671-8875-fd8a4345f05e"}}
