{"type":"message","id":"7349ba5b","parentId":"375e0dd8","timestamp":"2026-04-17T15:45:28.782Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_CI6dfNwwnkSvRFzKwGQxvK3E|fc_0aa356ee13d07a430169e2559631e4819aaf73f12dc5960658","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: akshare-stock\ndescription: A股量化数据分析工具，基于AkShare库获取A股行情、财务数据、板块信息等。用于回答关于A股股票查询、行情数据、财务分析、选股等问题。\n---\n\n# A股量化 - AkShare 数据接口\n\n## 快速开始\n\n安装依赖：\n```bash\npip install akshare\n```\n\n## 支持的功能\n\n### 1. 实时行情查询（优先快接口）\n\n```python\nimport akshare as ak\n\n# 单票实时行情（推荐，通常 <1s）\nquote_df = ak.stock_bid_ask_em(symbol=\"301333\")\nquote = {row[\"item\"]: row[\"value\"] for _, row in quote_df.iterrows()}\nprint(\"最新价:\", quote.get(\"最新\"))\nprint(\"涨跌幅:\", quote.get(\"涨幅\"))\nprint(\"昨收:\", quote.get(\"昨收\"))\n\n# 需要按名称模糊匹配股票代码时，再用全市场快照（约 8~15s）\nall_df = ak.stock_zh_a_spot()\nall_df[all_df[\"名称\"].str.contains(\"诺思格\", na=False)]\n```\n\n### 2. 历史K线数据\n\n```python\nimport akshare as ak\n\n# 日K线\nstock_zh_a_hist(symbol=\"000001\", period=\"daily\", start_date=\"20240101\", end_date=\"20241231\", adjust=\"qfq\")\n\n# 周K线\nstock_zh_a_hist(symbol=\"000001\", period=\"weekly\", start_date=\"20240101\", end_date=\"20241231\", adjust=\"qfq\")\n\n# 月K线\nstock_zh_a_hist(symbol=\"000001\", period=\"monthly\", start_date=\"20240101\", end_date=\"20241231\", adjust=\"qfq\")\n```\n\n### 3. 财务数据\n\n```python\nimport akshare as ak\n\n# 财务报表\nstock_financial_abstract_ths(symbol=\"000001\", indicator=\"按报告期\")\n\n# 主要财务指标\nstock_financial_analysis_indicator(symbol=\"000001\")\n```\n\n### 4. 板块/行业分析\n\n```python\nimport akshare as ak\n\n# 行业板块行情\nstock_board_industry_name_em()\n\n# 概念板块行情\nstock_board_concept_name_em()\n\n# 板块内个股\nstock_board_industry_cons_em(symbol=\"半导体\")\n```\n\n### 5. 资金流向\n\n```python\nimport akshare as ak\n\n# 个股资金流向\nstock_individual_fund_flow(stock=\"000001\", market=\"sh\")\n\n# 大单净流入\nstock_individual_fund_flow(stock=\"000001\", market=\"sh\", symbol=\"大单净流入\")\n```\n\n### 6. 龙虎榜\n\n```python\nimport akshare as ak\n\n# 每日龙虎榜\nstock_lhb_detail_em(date=\"20240930\")\n\n# 机构调研\nstock_zlzj_em()\n```\n\n### 7. 新股/IPO\n\n```python\nimport akshare as ak\n\n# 新股申购\nstock_new_ipo_em()\n\n# 待上市新股\nstock_new_ipo_start_em()\n```\n\n### 8. 融资融券\n\n```python\nimport akshare as ak\n\n# 融资融券\nstock_margin_sse(symbol=\"600000\")\n\n# 融资融券明细\nstock_rzrq_detail_em(symbol=\"600000\", date=\"20240930\")\n```\n\n## 常用股票代码\n\n- **平安银行**: 000001\n- **贵州茅台**: 600519\n- **宁德时代**: 300750\n- **比亚迪**: 002594\n- **招商银行**: 600036\n\n## 备选方案: Baostock\n\n如果 AkShare 安装失败，可使用 baostock（更轻量）:\n\n```python\nimport baostock as bs\n\n# 登录\nlg = bs.login()\nprint(lg.error_msg)\n\n# 获取历史K线\nrs = bs.query_history_k_data_plus('sh.600519',\n    'date,code,open,high,low,close,volume',\n    start_date='20250101',\n    end_date='20251231')\n\ndata_list = []\nwhile rs.next:\n    data_list.append(rs.get_row_data())\n    \nbs.logout()\n```\n\n## 注意事项\n\n1. 数据仅供学术研究，不构成投资建议\n2. 接口可能因目标网站变动而失效\n3. 建议添加异常处理和重试机制\n4. **当前环境网络问题可能导致测试失败，请在本地环境测试**\n5. **单票查询禁止默认使用 `stock_zh_a_spot_em()`，该接口会抓取全市场，常见耗时 60~90 秒**\n6. 飞书对话优先返回结论：若查询超过 15 秒，先给阶段性结论，再继续深挖\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776440728767}}
{"type":"message","id":"758ae5df","parentId":"7349ba5b","timestamp":"2026-04-17T15:45:39.853Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering stock comparison**\n\nI need to act and compute a basic quantitative comparison with local data. It seems like utilizing akshare could work if there's network access, but there are timeouts to external networks. I wonder if local data in the project will be sufficient. I need to compare three stocks using the user's quantitative system, so I should check existing local daily data. Maybe I can inspect a file named a_stock_history.csv? Let's search for it!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0aa356ee13d07a430169e2559dbf4c819aaa2ced7c2a9d56e7\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp4lWhFw2CeScee5K5ysu3kMRRqLgRT97hWBv5pO_oaIhcZqeli2FC8erZd_6RlnFvk4zoaEcO5MwbFjZjiToyJKenhpj3HUR0dI1b6pLa5cggRMkEfuhgeccOIDzin9dI-n7QO90dWDdmpGrjaWXMH0n58Vj9CyTa5NfgitGpm87qUnjIVAjcYzUC7Y4MUrChQq_xPkhliuYZ9lBbjIOyP2LCV4UUoR7b15FC5Ww4imOb95qy5phll6NUR9PxGaWqQNDjYJJPnZUAA3UH9mYbMHdUem3QBBKZP-BFOBsu9zeQ2v6WOgCgDeokW2qBJFBrBG--qvLTGIWozkOB-h0ZMybMKXqSvT8TuP4RZ1DDL8XikfhzoECEtTKlLdamSqtlDQEA7NAPIF-ZL658ddz4HCX5qpx4_eh2CXfARg2mCrHG6gZdH1i5iR3VKt6AGyZFFJEpWKwKfCJUTLn3S8NN6bUIPFFmcJ-BA1ky_o59jFYiSPbuJ5-DpWuel7yykIM8R24i9hsOyZL1Zkmy6RgWny04FZVYbCwKO2dg9PgyK8CcYOnkFasaUJ0Wx_Ld3e_ygeqfki9XpGMUwMXupyp6sUbU9wYolcmixERMKpFiWy17ZBeVoAiVrWk1OU7gSXZZy5mDjwUUgh72SY5W_SYLhh0U3aClR_qYk1qpuHIrh8WRsVjFuQDSoQAdw1rB_m6FcqMXCfk6yjmpPXD4Y7RACI06voEiR0x3PE-9gV0VVHfdDakohkTJvZSjq5Q09lxTeSpHRazf4RT6bYy_TaB6GO0NM10r1Z0H6-0huyfpkisHV853W17fuWFZJ9JdKCmWXCvFJPqfVauuRmEI02SpArnskJo2viLItlgRjb8quoIWqUjMqjDIqh8DS97ew7pzew6lzl_Lpl5RuEjku7Yip1tSNkHt7UUA2e91jLxkD7gMHUL6zPuyehP2LldNulKaFyMJi_4_aYFqTAWiKlxZLI-IGTrWr8YtX29_p9JwCYq6WCmD1yzKsoyHtZ-gqdFDopkDFprQgDhc6lXiGQeEpMPVDz3yD1wYvu9lOoAtj_befAbzhbsc33EnrG2vBvxt5L-psFTJwbOF7ff-yXvEI3likHLPTnwQ3krAlxWoZ2SaRvC9H18gZtvJ0Aj111PN1ENX7OuuWdNGFFtcSsbY7hneKti3vO5x_5He2A6WhhLXkM8mSNQ2mE-3w8A3S_T0z